##"We ate like crazy because we didn't have a fridge. "

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Cha Qiongfang, the first group of Shanghai Support Hubei Medical Team members, Shanghai Jiaotong University Hospital affiliated Yan Chai attending physician

March 6, Day forty-two of support for Hubei, Cloudy Day in Wuhan.

Today's overcast, but to eat the home of our hearts is happy to bloom. Since last night, we began to taste the food cooked by the chef Jinjiang, which we seldom have the chance to eat even in Shanghai, let alone with a big dish full of love.

There's a reason it's crazy. These foods have a shelf life of two days, three days, and the longest XO sauce is only at room temperature for six days. In line with can not let down the love, can not waste the principle of food, in the absence of refrigerator preservation, the best way is into their own stomach!

The guys would bring their share into the restaurant, and they would try to hang a plastic bag in the window for a few more days, but more often they would just eat.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Food from home has a shelf life, and without a fridge, Kaifeng has a short shelf life. This article is illustrated by Cha Jongfang

The group of teachers that what to eat what the day of the good-natured reminder, so that we have a sense of urgency. Ha Ha, this is also "sweet burden" AH!

After a lavish breakfast of rice porridge with eight-treasure Chili Sauce and crab powder, we continued the feast at the entrance of the hotel. This time Dr. Zhou and I went a little further and came across the street. The same mall doors are closed, KFC, Watson's, children's Park are closed doors. The only open is a hotel door, in the hotel door, we saw the Shanghai brand car, a closer look, the original is the Shanghai Oriental Hospital's National Emergency Medical Rescue Team car.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Oriental Hospital National Emergency Medical Rescue Team vehicles parked in front of the hotel.

Life is everywhere meet Ah! The Wuhan Living Room of the Oriental Hospital is next to the Marriott Hotel where we used to live. It is across the street from the hospital. Now, far from home, to see the cars in Shanghai let me feel warm up.

At noon, I still brought home dishes into the restaurant, today's restaurant for everyone prepared "Wuchang Fish. ".

After lunch, we drank the white fungus peach jelly which the hotel manager had specially prepared for us. Yesterday we just drank the warm stomach brown sugar ginger tea, it seems that manager Chen prepared to "spoil" US AH.

Today night shift, I had a good sleep in the afternoon, wake up after a video with the home once again is told to drink more water, more rest, eat more fruit, eat more food. Can I not eat this much love?

Before going to work, I received a greeting from Shi Yang, a logistics teacher from Yan Chai Hospital in Thor Mountain. He said that he would bring our four-member team from Jin Yin Tan Hospital in Yan Chai tonight. Is Our RENJI canteen Shen Dacheng to do the vacuum packaging of delicious food, there are four Xi Baked Bran, there are braised bamboo shoots...

Today's Day, in the hometown of the food spent, thanks to the makers of each delicious food. At night, with a full stomach will continue to three female night watch.

I hope every patient is safe and sound, and I hope the night is no different.

(by C.C. Chan, _ paper _)
